   "source": [
    "## About the dataset\n",
    "\n",
    "This dataset contains appointment records and shows whether each patient attended or missed the visit.\n",
    "It includes patient demographics (age, gender), social factor (scholarship), and health indicators (hypertension, diabetes, alcoholism, handicap).\n",
    "It also includes scheduling information (scheduled date vs appointment date), which allows us to calculate waiting time.\n",
    "I chose this dataset because missed appointments affect clinic workflow, resource planning, and patient care.\n",
    "As a pharmacist, I find it relevant because missed visits can lead to missed monitoring and weaker follow-up for chronic patients."
   ]
